         MACRO
         OPSIZE &OPERAND
.*
.*       THE OPSIZE MACRO IS AN INNER MACRO INSTRUCTION WHICH
.*       RETURNS THE K' VALUE OF THE OPERAND PASSED TO IT IN THE
.*       GLOBAL ARITHMETIC VARIABLE &OPSIZE.
.*
.*G L O B A L   A R I T H M E T I C   V A R I A B L E S
.*
         GBLA  &OPSIZE
.*
.* S E T   S I Z E   O F   O P E R A N D
.*
&OPSIZE  SETA  K'&OPERAND
         MEND
